    "A Hugging Face token lets you push the dataset from the browser window. It is stored in the macOS Keychain.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hugging Face Token 可讓你從瀏覽器視窗推送資料集。它儲存於 macOS Keychain。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A few things are still pending — you can finish them now or later in Settings.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "還有幾項尚未完成，你可以現在處理，或之後在「設定」中完成。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A small popup appears. Start talking.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
