    "Auto cleans only clips it detects as noisy; On always cleans (DeepFilterNet).": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「自動」只清理偵測到有噪音的片段;「開啟」則一律清理(DeepFilterNet)。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Auto inspects each recording and denoises only noisy clips; On always denoises (DeepFilterNet). Downloads a small model on first use.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "自動會檢查每段錄音、只對吵雜的片段降噪；開啟則一律降噪（DeepFilterNet）。首次使用會下載一個小型模型。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
