    "Denoiser": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "降噪器"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Denoising runs at 48 kHz before the audio is downsampled for the ASR model. Auto only denoises clips it detects as noisy (and loads the model lazily on the first such clip); On always denoises. Use Benchmark to compare Off / Auto / On.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "降噪會在音訊降採樣給 ASR 模型之前以 48 kHz 執行。自動只對偵測為吵雜的片段降噪（並在第一個這種片段時才延遲載入模型）；開啟則一律降噪。可用 Benchmark 比較 關閉／自動／開啟。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Denoising runs at 48 kHz before the audio is downsampled for the ASR model. Best for noisy environments; may not help (or slightly hurt) clean recordings — use Benchmark to compare.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "降噪會在音訊被降採樣給 ASR 模型之前以 48 kHz 執行。最適合吵雜環境；對乾淨錄音可能無感（甚至略有損害）——可用 Benchmark 比較。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
