    "Lets ThinkAloud paste the transcription into the focused app. Optional — without it, text is copied to your clipboard instead (press ⌘V). After you enable it in System Settings, this updates on its own.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "讓 ThinkAloud 將轉錄結果貼到目前使用中的 App。此為選用;若未授予,文字會改為複製到剪貼簿(按 ⌘V)。在「系統設定」中啟用後,這裡會自動更新。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Lets ThinkAloud paste the transcription into the focused app. Optional — without it, text is copied to your clipboard instead.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
