    "Load keeps the model in memory for instant transcription; Unload frees it. Auto-unload releases the weights after the chosen idle time and reloads on next use.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「載入」會將模型保留在記憶體中以便即時轉錄;「卸載」則釋放它。「閒置時自動釋放」會在所選的閒置時間後釋放權重,並於下次使用時重新載入。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
