    "Pick the model that fits your Mac. It downloads once and runs on-device. You can switch anytime in Settings.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "挑選適合你 Mac 的模型。只需下載一次，並在本機執行。你隨時可在「設定」中切換。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pick the transcription engine — tap a model to make it active. Larger models are more accurate but slower and bigger on disk. The active model downloads on first use; download or remove variants here.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "選擇轉錄引擎 — 點一下模型即設為使用中。較大的模型更準確,但較慢、佔用更多磁碟空間。使用中的模型會在首次使用時下載;可在此下載或移除各種模型。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
