    "Start recording fires from anywhere to open the popup. Stop & transcribe and Insert & save both default to ⌥Space — the popup phase decides which one fires.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「開始錄音」可在任何地方觸發以開啟彈出視窗。「停止並轉錄」與「插入並儲存」皆預設為 ⌥Space — 由彈出視窗當下的階段決定觸發哪一個。"
          }
        }
