            "state": "translated",
            "value": "更新"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Updates are downloaded from GitHub Releases and verified with a cryptographic signature before installing.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "更新會從 GitHub Releases 下載，並在安裝前以密碼學簽章驗證。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Updates are downloaded from GitHub Releases and verified with a cryptographic signature before installing. The Dev channel tracks the latest main build and may be less stable; switching back to Stable takes effect once Stable's build number catches up.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "更新會從 GitHub Releases 下載，並在安裝前以密碼學簽章驗證。開發版頻道追蹤最新的 main 建置，可能較不穩定；切回正式版會在正式版的建置編號追上後才生效。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Uploaded %lld file(s) to %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "已上傳 %lld 個檔案至 %@。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Uploaded as `metadata.jsonl` + audio files (LFS). Audio is uploaded — only push if you've reviewed the contents.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "上傳成 `metadata.jsonl` + 音訊檔（走 LFS）。音檔會一同上傳——推送前請確認沒有敏感內容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Uploading large files…": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "上傳大檔案中…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use 3 days in a row": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "連續 3 天使用"
