          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Whisper Turbo"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Without Accessibility access, ThinkAloud copies the text to your clipboard instead of pasting it — just press ⌘V.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "若未授予輔助使用權限，ThinkAloud 會改為將文字複製到剪貼簿，按 ⌘V 貼上即可。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Word Error Rate — CJK ideographs count as words; 0 means perfect, lower is better.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "詞錯誤率（WER）—— 中日韓表意字各算一個詞；0 為完美，越低越好。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Word replacements": {
